OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776708666
OL,3,CParamedic university courses paused
OL,4,Cdue to lack of job opportunities
OL,6,FThere will be no paramedic university
OL,7,Fcourses run in Wales for the upcoming
OL,8,Facademic year in order "to reduce
OL,9,Fcompetition for vacancies".
OL,11,FHealth Education and Improvement Wales
OL,12,F(HEIW) made the announcement on Monday
OL,13,F(20 April).
OL,15,FCurrently, Swansea University and
OL,16,FWrexham University offer Paramedic
OL,17,FScience courses.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
