OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776708666
OL,3,CParamedic university courses paused
OL,4,Cdue to lack of job opportunities
OL,6,FAt the start of this month the Welsh
OL,7,FAmbulance Service said it is "not in a
OL,8,Fposition to employ newly qualified
OL,9,Fparamedics this year".
OL,11,FSeveral graduates told ITV News they
OL,12,Ffeel "extremely disappointed" after
OL,13,F"sacrificing so much time" undergoing
OL,14,Fspecialist paramedic training, only to
OL,15,Fdiscover there are no available jobs.
OL,17,FHEIW recognised it was an "uncertain
OL,18,Ftime" for students and graduates.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776708666
OL,3,CParamedic university courses paused
OL,4,Cdue to lack of job opportunities
OL,6,FIn a statement they said: "Pausing new
OL,7,Fstudent intake is considered the most
OL,8,Fresponsible step to reduce competition
OL,9,Ffor vacancies over the next few years,
OL,10,Fand support current and upcoming
OL,11,Fgraduates into employment.
OL,13,F"HEIW and WAST are working closely to
OL,14,Fidentify potential employment
OL,15,Fopportunities in ambulance services
OL,16,Fand across wider health and care
OL,17,Fsettings. Some graduates might still
OL,18,Fsecure paramedic roles, but this may
OL,19,Ftake time.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776708666
OL,3,CParamedic university courses paused
OL,4,Cdue to lack of job opportunities
OL,6,F"In addition, support is also being
OL,7,Fdeveloped for recent graduates to
OL,8,Fmaintain clinical skills and
OL,9,Fcompetence, access continuing
OL,10,Fprofessional development, and explore
OL,11,Fpotential alternative career pathways.
OL,12,FThis will help ensure when Paramedic
OL,13,Fvacancies become available, recent
OL,14,Fgraduates will be able to move into
OL,15,Fthem.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
