PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776708666
OL,3,CParamedic university courses paused
OL,4,Cdue to lack of job opportunities
OL,6,F"HEIW also acknowledges concerns
OL,7,Fregarding NHS Wales bursary repayment.
OL,8,FThe bursary terms and conditions
OL,9,Finclude provision for individuals to
OL,10,Fbe released from repayment
OL,11,Frequirements where appropriate."
OL,13,FBoth Swansea University and Wrexham
OL,14,FUniversity have been approached for
OL,15,Fcomment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
